  description: "asyncio.get_event_loop.__doc__ contains checks in ae213gel namespace — wave 213 theme: asyncio.get_event_loop.__doc__.__contains__('event')==True ('Return an asyncio event loop.' — 'event' in 'event loop'); asyncio.get_event_loop.__doc__.__contains__('loop')==True ('loop' appears in 'event loop'); asyncio.get_event_loop.__doc__.__len__()==306 (306-char docstring describing when to use get_event_loop vs get_running_loop); verified with Python 3.14.3"
  kind: python_call_eq
  category: identity
